summary.label:
BEBOPS are getting together for a big concert and need your help to choose who is going to play on stage!

With dozens of musicians (each with 3 variations) you can have endless combinations and create all sorts of addictive tunes. 

There are countless possibilities to explore! Orchestra players, rock stars, but also the characters from your favourite Fairy Tales - Snow White, the Prince Charming, Puss on Boots - or even cute, fluffy animals will make this the best musical experience for kids of all ages!

The children friendly interface allows kids to play easily and have fun without the need of parents' help or guidance. And with no in-app purchases, it's 100% safe to let them play!

- 165 musicians, each with their own unique, original sounds and moves!
- 11 BEBOPS styles available: New jazz / Animals / Fantasy / Monsters / Rock / Robots / Cavemen / Samba / Hip Hop / Reggae / Techno;
- Change the way characters play by touching on them;
- Adjust volume (long press characters);
- Incredible graphics and animations;
- Child friendly interface;

We take privacy seriously. The BEBOPS app:
- Does NOT contain ads;
- Does NOT contain in-app purchases;
- Does NOT share any information with third party;
- Does NOT collect or store personal information.
